vernac_cmds: Module fc_preservation (wf : fc_wf_sig) (weak : fc_weak_sig) (subst : fc_subst_sig) (e_subst : ext_subst_sig).
Module invert := fc_invert wf weak subst.
Lemma open_a_Conv : forall a b g, open_tm_wrt_tm (a_Conv a g) b = a_Conv (open_tm_wrt_tm a b) (open_co_wrt_tm g b).
Lemma open_a_Conv_co : forall a b g, open_tm_wrt_co (a_Conv a g) b = a_Conv (open_tm_wrt_co a b) (open_co_wrt_co g b).

Ltac lc_erase_hyp := match goal with | H : AnnTyping ?G ?a ?A0 |- lc_tm (erase_tm ?a) => eapply lc_erase; apply (AnnTyping_lc H) | H : AnnTyping ?G ?a ?A0 |- lc_tm ?a => apply (AnnTyping_lc1 H) | H : lc_tm ?a |- lc_tm (erase ?a) => eapply lc_erase; eauto | H : lc_tm (a_Abs ?r ?a ?b) |- lc_tm ?c => apply lc_erase in H; simpl in H; auto | H : lc_tm (a_CAbs ?a ?b) |- lc_tm ?c => apply lc_erase in H; simpl in H; auto end.
Lemma binds_toplevel: forall F a A, binds F (Ax a A) an_toplevel -> binds F (Ax (erase a) (erase A)) toplevel.
eapply binds_map with (f:= erase_csort) in H.

Ltac do_rho := match goal with H : ∀ x : atom, x `notin` ?L → RhoCheck Irrel x (erase_tm (open_tm_wrt_tm ?b (a_Var_f x))) |- ?x `notin` fv_tm_tm_tm (open_tm_wrt_tm (erase ?b) (a_Var_f ?x)) => let h := fresh in let F := fresh in assert (F : x `notin` L); auto; move: (H x F) => h; inversion h; subst; replace (a_Var_f x) with (erase (a_Var_f x)); auto; rewrite open_tm_erase_tm; auto end.
Ltac eauto_lc := simpl; eauto using AnnTyping_lc1, Value_lc, AnnDefEq_lc3, AnnPropWff_lc.
Lemma head_reduction_in_one : forall G a b, head_reduction G a b -> forall A, AnnTyping G a A -> reduction_in_one (erase a) (erase b) \/ erase a = erase b.
move: lc_erase => [lc_er_tm _] G a b H.
induction H; intros AA TT ; inversion TT; try (simpl; eauto).
assert (Ax a A = Ax a0 AA).
Lemma head_reduction_erased : forall G a b, head_reduction G a b -> forall A, AnnTyping G a A -> Par G (dom G) (erase a) (erase b).
induction H; intros AA TT ; inversion TT; try (simpl; econstructor; eauto).
match goal with H : AnnTyping ?G (a_Abs Irrel ?A ?b) (a_Pi Irrel ?A0 ?B) |- _ => inversion H; clear H end.
match goal with H : lc_tm (a_Abs Irrel ?A0 ?b) |- lc_tm (a_UAbs Irrel (erase ?b)) => eapply lc_erase in H; simpl in H; auto end.
apply binds_map with (f := erase_csort) in H.
match goal with H : AnnTyping ?G (a_Conv ?v ?g1) ?A |- lc_tm (erase_tm ?v) => inversion H end.
destruct rho; subst; simpl; eauto using lc_erase.
Lemma preservation : forall G a A, AnnTyping G a A -> forall a', head_reduction G a a' -> AnnTyping G a' A.
pick fresh x and apply An_Abs; eauto 3.
have RC: RhoCheck Irrel x (erase_tm (open_tm_wrt_tm a (a_Var_f x))); eauto.
have HR: head_reduction ([(x, Tm A)] ++ G) (open_tm_wrt_tm a (a_Var_f x)) (open_tm_wrt_tm b' (a_Var_f x)); eauto.
have Ta: AnnTyping ([(x, Tm A)] ++ G) (open_tm_wrt_tm b' (a_Var_f x)) (open_tm_wrt_tm B (a_Var_f x)); eauto.
eapply An_Trans with (a1 := A); eauto 2 using AnnTyping_regularity.
assert (Ax a A = Ax a' A0).
eapply AnnTyping_weakening with (F:=nil)(G:=nil)(E:=G) in H4; eauto.

command: eapply binds_map with (f:= erase_csort) in H.
